2
00:01:29,770 --> 00:01:31,180
[My Journey to You]

3
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,050
[Episode 9]

4
00:01:40,289 --> 00:01:40,800
Father!

5
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,450
I don't want to go in.

6
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,100
It's cold inside.

7
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:47,229
No.

8
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,390
Young Master.

9
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:00,860
Yun.

10
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:03,310
Did I fall asleep?

11
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:07,200
You fainted from the cold.

12
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:10,820
I told you not to act tough or be impatient,

13
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,040
but you still acted recklessly.

14
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:14,860
If I hadn't come,

15
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:16,450
you might have

16
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:19,079
frozen to death in that ice bucket.

17
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,560
Why are your hands so hot?

18
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,030
I've had a nickname

19
00:02:36,290 --> 00:02:37,350
since I was little,

20
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,530
called Little Furnace.

21
00:02:39,790 --> 00:02:41,120
Why would a girl like you

22
00:02:41,390 --> 00:02:42,920
have such a nickname?

23
00:02:44,230 --> 00:02:45,340
My family said

24
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:47,760
that my mother had reached the full term

25
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,850
of pregnancy with me,

26
00:02:48,850 --> 00:02:50,510
but there was no sign of birth.

27
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:53,310
I wasn't born until a dozen days later.

28
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:55,820
They teased

29
00:02:55,930 --> 00:02:57,480
that I was well-cooked.

30
00:02:57,970 --> 00:02:59,020
What a coincidence.

31
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,090
I had a premature birth,

32
00:03:00,090 --> 00:03:01,430
so I tend to be cold.

33
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:03,750
With the two of us,

34
00:03:04,230 --> 00:03:05,150
one is like ice

35
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,680
and the other is like fire.

36
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,610
We are a match made in...

37
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,090
Made in...

38
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:25,180
Yun,

39
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:26,980
you just said

40
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:30,200
it was you who pulled me out of the ice bucket.

41
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:33,360
I couldn't carry you by myself,

42
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:35,240
so I asked some servants

43
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:36,790
to help lift you out.

44
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:41,850
Young Master Ziyu.

45
00:03:46,210 --> 00:03:47,340
You saw everything?

46
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:55,600
Yes.

47
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,640
I only saw your chest.

48
00:04:05,350 --> 00:04:06,690
You're a man.

49
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,180
This is nothing.

50
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,050
Besides,

51
00:04:12,010 --> 00:04:13,770
I'm already married to you.

52
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,779
We're not married yet.

53
00:04:21,339 --> 00:04:22,600
Won't you ask me

54
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:25,820
why I came to see you in the middle of the night?

55
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:30,910
How would I know?

56
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,640
Young Master,

57
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,180
what are you thinking?

58
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:40,980
You asked me

59
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:42,620
why you came to me.

60
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,450
What?

61
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:50,100
I came to tell you

62
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,320
I seem to have found

63
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:54,159
the way to pass the first trial.

64
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,850
Really?

65
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:02,090
There are hundreds of mental techniques in the world,

66
00:05:02,090 --> 00:05:03,460
but they can be roughly divided into

67
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:05,270
metal, wood, water, fire, and earth.

68
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:06,360
[Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, Earth]

69
00:05:05,410 --> 00:05:06,410
These five types.

70
00:05:06,670 --> 00:05:07,750
These five types

71
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:10,010
can be further divided into yin and yang.

72
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:12,200
Among them, metal and fire techniques

73
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,060
are the Supreme Yang techniques,

74
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:16,610
such as the Yang-Splitting Chant of the Kunlun Sect

75
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:19,070
and the Metal Language of the Cangshan Sect.

76
00:05:19,590 --> 00:05:22,180
Water and wood techniques are the Supreme Yin techniques,

77
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:22,910
such as

78
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,020
the Brocade Heart Sutra of the Qingfeng Sect,

79
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:27,240
and the Water Avoidance Art of the Blackwater Sect.

80
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,970
Furthermore, the Yijin Manual

81
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,690
has an earth attribute.

82
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,750
It includes both yin and yang,

83
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,780
integrating all.

84
00:05:34,510 --> 00:05:36,260
If the Gong residence's mental techniques

85
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:37,659
are under metal and fire,

86
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:40,560
then the Ice Pool can naturally be overcome.

87
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,270
This coincides

88
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,710
with what Jin Fan said.

89
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,420
The first trial

90
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:47,330
seems to ask you

91
00:05:47,370 --> 00:05:50,540
to find the Snow Saber Scripture at the bottom of the Ice Pool,

92
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:51,740
but actually,

93
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:54,640
it is testing your internal skill.

94
00:05:58,130 --> 00:05:59,050
But

95
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:01,030
the Gong residence

96
00:06:01,590 --> 00:06:03,780
has multiple kinds of mental techniques.

97
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:04,980
We have so many kinds.

98
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:07,790
The Gong residence

99
00:06:07,790 --> 00:06:10,270
has created three unique mental techniques.

100
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,240
In addition,

101
00:06:11,590 --> 00:06:13,590
my ancestors had fought in the martial world for years

102
00:06:13,590 --> 00:06:15,850
and learned many top mental techniques.

103
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:17,430
Even

104
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,370
some long-lost mental techniques

105
00:06:19,370 --> 00:06:21,220
from major martial sects

106
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:23,890
are also recorded within the Gong residence.

107
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:26,090
It's just that we are not allowed to cultivate them.

108
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:27,040
Then,

109
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,730
which one do you cultivate?

110
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,460
Snowmelt Heart Sutra.

111
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,500
I've never heard of it.

112
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:41,620
It's a unique method created by the Gong residence.

113
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:42,950
Few people cultivate it

114
00:06:43,210 --> 00:06:45,010
even within the Gong residence.

115
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:48,420
Father,

116
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:49,690
it's too cold.

117
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,740
I can't stand it anymore.

118
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:54,409
If you don't want to be frozen, use the chant.

119
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,240
I've memorized it long ago,

120
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:58,930
but it's too cold. I can't recite it.

121
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,240
You're too weak.

122
00:07:00,610 --> 00:07:02,270
You don't deserve to be my son.

123
00:07:04,330 --> 00:07:05,660
Look at how your brother

124
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:07,070
practices martial arts.

125
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:20,740
Cold air...

126
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,600
Cold air enters the clouds.

127
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,900
The reception and delivery must be controlled.

128
00:07:26,350 --> 00:07:27,810
You're not allowed to cry.

129
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:30,800
Continue.

130
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,570
Gather in the core.

131
00:07:34,409 --> 00:07:35,020
Snow...

132
00:07:35,470 --> 00:07:37,400
Snow falls, but the heart does not.

133
00:07:38,909 --> 00:07:40,770
Both enter the Fengmen acupoint.

134
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,090
The pulse nears the end point.

135
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:45,740
That's great.

136
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,000
It's not great.

137
00:07:50,050 --> 00:07:51,100
My internal skill

138
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:52,150
can't even hold up

139
00:07:52,150 --> 00:07:53,550
against the winter wind,

140
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:56,040
let alone dive to the bottom of the Ice Pool.

141
00:07:58,790 --> 00:08:00,390
After my mother passed away,

142
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,710
my father

143
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,760
became stricter and colder to me.

144
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:07,600
I was born with cold intolerance,

145
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,270
but my father forced me

146
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:11,330
to practice in frigid environments.

147
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:12,860
So,

148
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:14,900
I always resisted

149
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:17,470
cultivating the Snowmelt Heart Sutra

150
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:20,260
and gave up later.

151
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:27,530
The ginger tea is cold.

152
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:28,890
I'll heat it up for you.

153
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:30,750
It's okay.

154
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,350
I'm not afraid of this kind of cold.

155
00:08:42,190 --> 00:08:43,700
Young Master, do you think

156
00:08:44,169 --> 00:08:45,340
that the former Sword Wielder

157
00:08:45,340 --> 00:08:46,790
was too heartless to you?

158
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,200
Do you remember what I told you

159
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:55,620
about my father's shipwreck?

160
00:08:57,110 --> 00:08:58,310
Of course I remember.

161
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:00,830
I misunderstood you at that time.

162
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:02,590
I thought you set the river lantern

163
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:04,170
to send some news out.

164
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,470
After my father passed away,

165
00:09:07,990 --> 00:09:10,720
my mother supported the whole family by herself.

166
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:12,870
After that,

167
00:09:13,690 --> 00:09:15,720
my mother, who once doted on me,

168
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,160
gradually became strict.

169
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:22,590
Is that similar to your situation?

170
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,750
When I was young,

171
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,330
I used to ride horses with my godmother, Zhuo Mei,

172
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:31,820
and practice swordsmanship

173
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:32,820
and martial arts.

174
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,890
I was as free as a boy.

175
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:39,260
But after my father's death,

176
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:42,660
my mother started forcing me to the learn women's virtues.

177
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:45,470
Every day, I had to practice needlework,

178
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:48,270
instruments, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

179
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:51,520
Mother said

180
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:55,310
that Zhuo Mei had extraordinary swordsmanship,

181
00:09:55,310 --> 00:09:57,040
but she lived a miserable life.

182
00:09:58,140 --> 00:10:00,390
If I can't protect myself by learning martial arts,

183
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,520
it's better to marry into a good family

184
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:04,770
and protect my whole clan.

185
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:09,640
Mother told me every day

186
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:12,430
that a woman

187
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:14,700
can't live on her own.

188
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,520
Later,

189
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,400
I gradually gave up

190
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,240
and accepted myself

191
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:27,710
as a tool for my mother to climb up the social ranks.

192
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:30,480
But in my heart,

193
00:10:32,050 --> 00:10:34,070
a voice continued to tell me

194
00:10:35,730 --> 00:10:36,740
that a person

195
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,730
only lives once.

196
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:42,850
I should live the way I like.

197
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:46,020
A skylark

198
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:49,470
should call out in the valley,

199
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,420
listen to the rain,

200
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:55,620
and smell the fragrant flowers,

201
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:59,620
instead of singing in a cage.

202
00:11:03,650 --> 00:11:04,260
So,

203
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:06,510
I told my mother

204
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,610
I just want to live for myself.

205
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:16,150
I don't want to be anyone's accessory.

206
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:21,240
What right do you have to say no?

207
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,690
Since I have no right to say no,

208
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,670
then why am I practicing this?

209
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,000
You are practicing this

210
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,310
so that one day,

211
00:11:30,290 --> 00:11:31,720
you can say no to others.

212
00:11:37,730 --> 00:11:38,510
That's why

213
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:42,770
you kept wanting to escape from the Gong residence.

214
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:50,250
But later, I realized

215
00:11:51,740 --> 00:11:53,570
that my mother was just worried that our family

216
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:54,700
only has women left.

217
00:11:56,390 --> 00:11:57,730
We no longer have someone

218
00:11:57,730 --> 00:11:59,080
who can support us.

219
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:03,320
She was afraid that I'd be mistreated in the future.

220
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,850
You owe your life to Wufeng.

221
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:08,360
You also owe your skills to Wufeng.

222
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,730
As long as you're alive,

223
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:13,980
you must be useful to Wufeng.

224
00:12:14,580 --> 00:12:15,340
Even if you die,

225
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:17,270
you must still be useful to Wufeng.

226
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:23,450
I can't live the way I want,

227
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,450
but at the very least,

228
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:28,150
I can die as I wish.

229
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:31,030
You can,

230
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:33,960
but you dare not.

231
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,400
Why not?

232
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:39,630
Because you still have Yun Que.

233
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:42,520
As long as

234
00:12:43,950 --> 00:12:46,150
there is someone you love in this world,

235
00:12:46,730 --> 00:12:47,930
you won't dare to die.

236
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:54,330
If you don't want to have weaknesses,

237
00:12:55,230 --> 00:12:56,810
you must not love anyone.

238
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:00,920
In my mother's eyes,

239
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:04,510
the martial arts world filled with conflicts

240
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:06,310
is too difficult

241
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:08,600
for a woman.

242
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,750
So, to her,

243
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:15,580
the Gong family was what could be relied on.

244
00:13:15,930 --> 00:13:17,290
There is a mission now.

245
00:13:18,450 --> 00:13:19,580
You can leave Wufeng

246
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:23,390
once you complete it

247
00:13:24,540 --> 00:13:26,140
and get the freedom you want.

248
00:13:26,770 --> 00:13:28,770
Actually, the care given by parents

249
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:31,880
is like the delicate rain on a spring night,

250
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,480
replenishing soundlessly.

251
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:35,930
My strict mother

252
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,100
watched me suffer every day,

253
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:39,840
but she tried her best

254
00:13:40,380 --> 00:13:42,780
to bring me new gimmicks from the outside world

255
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,680
to cheer me up.

256
00:13:44,730 --> 00:13:45,990
Give it to your sister.

257
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,280
But she never said anything.

258
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:01,700
Our parents forced us to grow up,

259
00:14:02,950 --> 00:14:05,150
but it's not their original intention.

260
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:08,010
They just hope

261
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,380
that before they pass away,

262
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,870
we can learn more

263
00:14:15,810 --> 00:14:16,980
and be able to

264
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:19,720
safely survive in this world.

265
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:24,170
More than anything,

266
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:27,240
they wish we can be children forever.

267
00:14:30,300 --> 00:14:31,760
You're not young anymore.

268
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:33,300
You'd better think it over.

269
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:34,510
If

270
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:36,650
you want to continue being useless,

271
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:40,520
there's no need for you to stay in the Gong family anymore.

272
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:47,560
Did I overstep boundaries again?

273
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:50,120
No.

274
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:52,780
I like to hear you talk about

275
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:53,860
your past life.

276
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:56,800
I also like to hear about

277
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:57,960
the outside world.

278
00:15:02,890 --> 00:15:03,790
Young Master,

279
00:15:05,220 --> 00:15:06,820
have you never been outside?

280
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:10,120
Never.

281
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:14,870
If we have time in the future,

282
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,650
I will accompany you out to see it.

283
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:21,720
Okay.

284
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:29,870
But

285
00:15:30,030 --> 00:15:30,810
my back...

286
00:15:33,290 --> 00:15:35,060
After the secret text is tattooed,

287
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:38,020
you will never be able to leave the Jiuchen Valley.

288
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:42,030
You must live here for the rest of your life.

