do you know what you are doing?

575
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:56,740
Gong Ziyu,

576
00:30:57,620 --> 00:30:58,820
do you know what she is doing?

577
00:30:58,820 --> 00:30:59,870
Of course I do.

578
00:31:01,250 --> 00:31:03,100
Otherwise, why would I come to protect her?

579
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:03,900
That's great.

580
00:31:04,260 --> 00:31:05,010
Tell me.

581
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:05,980
How dare you, the Sword Wielder,

582
00:31:05,980 --> 00:31:07,540
send your unmarried wife

583
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,860
to infiltrate the clinic in the middle of the night

584
00:31:08,860 --> 00:31:10,520
and secretly create a poison?

585
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:11,670
Who is it for?

586
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:13,370
I'm the Sword Wielder.

587
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:15,640
I don't need to explain this to you.

588
00:31:40,980 --> 00:31:42,040
Young Master Ziyu,

589
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:44,620
were you

590
00:31:45,140 --> 00:31:47,800
waiting for me outside the clinic all this time?

591
00:31:48,460 --> 00:31:49,030
Yes.

592
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:51,400
I was worried about you,

593
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,450
so I followed you.

594
00:31:54,980 --> 00:31:56,980
It's heavily guarded here at night.

595
00:31:57,450 --> 00:31:59,450
I feared you would run into trouble.

596
00:32:00,710 --> 00:32:02,510
Then I heard a commotion inside,

597
00:32:02,870 --> 00:32:04,740
so I rushed in with Jin Fan.

598
00:32:08,190 --> 00:32:09,090
Thank you.

599
00:32:11,740 --> 00:32:12,540
Young Master,

600
00:32:14,050 --> 00:32:15,450
I prepared the medicine,

601
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:17,350
but the dosage is not enough.

602
00:32:18,090 --> 00:32:19,750
I'll make some more tomorrow.

603
00:32:20,210 --> 00:32:22,740
Is there not enough reserve in the warehouse?

604
00:32:23,300 --> 00:32:24,910
The Gong residence's pharmacy

605
00:32:24,910 --> 00:32:25,840
has everything.

606
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:27,370
But just now,

607
00:32:27,790 --> 00:32:29,640
Young Master Yuanzhi asked me to prove

608
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,430
that the medicine isn't poisonous,

609
00:32:31,430 --> 00:32:33,360
so he ordered me to drink half of it.

610
00:32:36,570 --> 00:32:37,570
Give me your hand.

611
00:32:41,090 --> 00:32:41,690
This is...

612
00:32:42,980 --> 00:32:43,780
Herb Elixir.

613
00:32:46,970 --> 00:32:48,570
Young Master, you'll give me

614
00:32:48,950 --> 00:32:50,170
something so precious?

615
00:32:50,170 --> 00:32:51,140
Rumor has it

616
00:32:51,430 --> 00:32:54,060
that one Herb Elixir is worth ten taels of gold,

617
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:56,900
but it doesn't have a market.

618
00:32:57,060 --> 00:32:58,190
No one has ever

619
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,460
bought a genuine Herb Elixir before.

620
00:33:01,070 --> 00:33:02,140
But for us,

621
00:33:04,060 --> 00:33:06,110
it's just an everyday object.

622
00:33:08,070 --> 00:33:09,120
If you take it now,

623
00:33:09,690 --> 00:33:11,750
it can remove the Supreme Cold poison

624
00:33:12,140 --> 00:33:13,700
you ingested for me.

625
00:33:15,090 --> 00:33:17,170
The Herb Elixir is the most effective

626
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:18,640
when taken daily

627
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:20,650
and it can protect you from the toxin

628
00:33:20,650 --> 00:33:21,980
before being poisoned.

629
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:25,930
But if you can take it promptly after being poisoned,

630
00:33:25,930 --> 00:33:28,190
it can also have most of the same effects.

631
00:33:30,670 --> 00:33:31,330
This poison

632
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:33,350
is extremely cold and painful,

633
00:33:34,290 --> 00:33:35,350
but it's not fatal.

634
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:38,020
I'll be fine after just one night.

635
00:33:40,630 --> 00:33:41,790
You should keep

636
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:44,230
this Herb Elixir for yourself.

637
00:33:45,020 --> 00:33:46,430
Don't waste

638
00:33:47,650 --> 00:33:49,330
something so precious on me.

639
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:54,440
It's not a waste

640
00:33:55,570 --> 00:33:56,890
as long as it's for you.

641
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:11,750
Besides,

642
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:14,370
according to our arrangement,

643
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:16,730
I should stop taking the Herb Elixir for a few days.

644
00:34:16,730 --> 00:34:17,989
Instead of wasting it,

645
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,719
I'd rather give it to you.

646
00:34:20,570 --> 00:34:21,100
Alright.

647
00:34:21,690 --> 00:34:22,510
Stop hesitating.

648
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,219
Take it.

649
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,080
What's wrong?

650
00:34:50,010 --> 00:34:50,929
It's dark.

651
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:52,570
Let me lead you.

652
00:35:08,870 --> 00:35:12,170
♫River lights, mountains dark, moon round♫

653
00:35:12,430 --> 00:35:15,510
♫Moonlight shines upon the mountain south♫

654
00:35:15,870 --> 00:35:17,320
♫My beloved♫

655
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:21,540
♫Gazes at me but with a river between us♫

656
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:26,100
♫The clouds and wind don't speak♫

657
00:35:26,350 --> 00:35:29,780
♫Love begins with a point in one's heart♫

658
00:35:30,220 --> 00:35:32,020
♫I have an empty room in my heart♫

659
00:35:32,050 --> 00:35:34,990
♫But it can't be filled by gold and silver♫

660
00:35:36,590 --> 00:35:42,890
♫A refuge in this world is rare♫

661
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:50,750
♫How the years go by with whitening hair♫

662
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:54,450
♫Listen to the shepherd boy's song♫

663
00:35:54,630 --> 00:35:57,970
♫Ask the flowers and leaves whom they fall for♫

664
00:35:58,100 --> 00:36:03,520
♫Wish moonlight can soothe the displaced ones♫

665
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:17,350
What's wrong?

666
00:36:19,050 --> 00:36:21,180
I bumped into Yun Weishan in the clinic

667
00:36:21,630 --> 00:36:23,960
and caught her in the act of making poison.

668
00:36:24,220 --> 00:36:26,880
But then Gong Ziyu used his Sword Wielder status

669
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:28,670
and took her away.

670
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:31,740
Yun Weishan

671
00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:33,190
produced poison?

672
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:33,940
Yes.

673
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:35,470
I saw her herbal residue.

674
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:39,260
It was gardenia, fire licorice, and amber with winter worms.

675
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:40,730
When boiling,

676
00:36:40,750 --> 00:36:42,680
she added cinnabar and saltpeter.

677
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:44,600
This is obviously the prescription

678
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,000
for a Supreme Yin poison.

679
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:48,770
It was turned into a lump of black residue

680
00:36:49,130 --> 00:36:51,930
and you could still distinguish the ingredients?

681
00:36:52,660 --> 00:36:53,190
Brother,

682
00:36:53,530 --> 00:36:54,870
others wouldn't know,

683
00:36:55,180 --> 00:36:56,190
but to me,

684
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:57,530
it's a piece of cake.

685
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,360
Did Gong Ziyu know

686
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:04,840
that Yun Weishan was producing poison?

687
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:06,470
That fool.

688
00:37:06,890 --> 00:37:08,750
He would say yes even if he didn't.

689
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:09,830
Brother,

690
00:37:10,170 --> 00:37:11,110
you should've seen how he was

691
00:37:11,110 --> 00:37:12,620
when he protected Yun Weishan.

692
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:13,380
Yun Weishan

693
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:16,320
is helping Gong Ziyu pass the Ice Pool trial.

694
00:37:17,540 --> 00:37:18,760
Ice Pool?

695
00:37:21,130 --> 00:37:21,910
What is this?

696
00:37:22,160 --> 00:37:23,210
The Ice Lotus Pool

697
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:26,360
is the first test of the Trial of the Three Realms.

698
00:37:27,060 --> 00:37:27,590
Brother,

699
00:37:28,740 --> 00:37:30,560
according to the Gong family's rules,

700
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:33,020
you probably shouldn't have told me, right?

701
00:37:34,830 --> 00:37:37,430
You've broken more than enough rules already.

702
00:37:37,980 --> 00:37:38,530
Besides,

703
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:41,940
I don't think I told you anything.

704
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,310
You're so nice to me.

705
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:47,880
Brother,

706
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:49,660
what's so special

707
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:50,760
about the Ice Pool?

708
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,580
It sounds mysterious.

709
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,540
Don't ask about it.

710
00:37:55,290 --> 00:37:56,490
When you are an adult

711
00:37:56,830 --> 00:37:58,890
and go to the back hill for the trials,

712
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:01,990
you'll naturally find out.

713
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:02,840
It's easy.

714
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:05,360
I won't be a loser like Gong Ziyu

715
00:38:05,590 --> 00:38:07,520
and be stuck in there for 3 or 4 days.

716
00:38:08,170 --> 00:38:10,500
Back then, I was trapped there for 12 days.

717
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:31,930
But Brother,

718
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:34,290
I don't want to be the Sword Wielder.

719
00:38:34,290 --> 00:38:35,170
You can do it.

720
00:38:36,050 --> 00:38:37,570
So, I don't have to do

721
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:39,520
the trials in the back hill.

722
00:38:41,370 --> 00:38:42,270
You must go.

723
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:46,260
If you don't want to be mistreated in the future,

724
00:38:46,260 --> 00:38:47,000
you must go.

725
00:38:49,650 --> 00:38:51,050
I'll do whatever you say.

726
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:56,190
By the way,

727
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:59,020
Yun Weishan's prescription

728
00:38:59,020 --> 00:39:00,680
was very complicated.

729
00:39:01,830 --> 00:39:04,760
It's not something that ordinary people can master.

730
00:39:04,820 --> 00:39:06,710
Also, I just fought with her.

731
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:09,900
Her martial arts skills aren't bad either.

732
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:11,580
I don't think

733
00:39:12,690 --> 00:39:14,940
she is Miss Yun from Lixi Town.

734
00:39:16,010 --> 00:39:17,610
Of course she's not.

735
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:19,610
However,

736
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:22,560
there are no flaws in her identity

737
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:26,060
and Gong Ziyu is protecting her with all his might.

738
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:27,620
Without solid evidence,

739
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:30,030
it's hard to do anything to her.

740
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:32,610
However,

741
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:36,120
the frost and dew are heavy in winter.

742
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:37,990
If you walk too much at night,

743
00:39:38,330 --> 00:39:39,790
things can get dangerous.

744
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:58,160
Are my hands a little cold?

745
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:01,600
I've been easily cold since childhood.

746
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,730
My body temperature

747
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,600
is always lower than the others.

748
00:40:05,510 --> 00:40:06,560
But Miss Yun,

749
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:08,580
your hands are so hot.

750
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:10,090
I envy you.

751
00:40:11,350 --> 00:40:12,760
What's there to envy?

752
00:40:14,590 --> 00:40:15,640
The elders say

753
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,240
the palm is the heart of the hand.

754
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,660
Those with warm hands

755
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:21,590
are also warm-hearted.

756
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:25,560
Young Master Ziyu, you look cold but are warm inside.

757
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:26,610
I can feel it.

758
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:28,760
You're the opposite of me.

759
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:30,680
On the contrary,

760
00:40:31,170 --> 00:40:32,550
I quite envy you.

761
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:35,730
The opposite?

762
00:40:37,070 --> 00:40:39,670
Then, do you have a warm surface but cold heart?

763
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:41,970
I can warm you up.

764
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,970
The snow is thick.

765
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:20,350
We are further into winter.

766
00:41:22,540 --> 00:41:23,870
Are you waiting for him?

767
00:41:28,310 --> 00:41:30,010
I believe he will come back.

768
00:41:43,500 --> 00:41:44,070
Jin Fan,

769
00:41:44,620 --> 00:41:45,680
where's Gong Ziyu?

770
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:48,380
Lord Sword Wielder went to the back hill early in the morning.

771
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:49,380
Is he okay?

772
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:51,090
He has been frowning

773
00:41:51,090 --> 00:41:52,730
ever since he returned from the back hill.

774
00:41:52,730 --> 00:41:55,000
His brows are all knitted together.

775
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:57,470
The Sword Wielder seems to be in good spirits.

776
00:41:57,470 --> 00:41:58,200
Don't worry.

777
00:41:58,500 --> 00:42:00,330
He seems to be confident about the Ice Pool.

778
00:42:00,330 --> 00:42:01,260
No wonder.

779
00:42:01,650 --> 00:42:03,900
I secretly heard the servants say

780
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:05,600
that Miss Yun stayed in his room

781
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:07,410
for half the night yesterday.

782
00:42:07,870 --> 00:42:09,130
It's all thanks to her.

783
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:12,030
The Sword Wielder and Miss Yun

784
00:42:12,030 --> 00:42:13,290
merely had a chat

785
00:42:13,550 --> 00:42:14,320
about their aspirations

786
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:15,330
and life.

787
00:42:15,350 --> 00:42:17,210
How do you know they were talking?

788
00:42:17,350 --> 00:42:18,610
You eavesdropped

789
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:19,910
while doing a handstand again?

790
00:42:19,910 --> 00:42:21,610
I have no time to waste with you.

791
00:42:21,610 --> 00:42:23,210
Lord Sword Wielder gave me a task.

792
00:42:23,210 --> 00:42:23,780
Goodbye.

793
00:42:23,990 --> 00:42:24,370
Okay.

794
00:42:24,810 --> 00:42:25,920
I'll go with you.

795
00:42:26,930 --> 00:42:27,860
Take me with you.

796
00:42:28,170 --> 00:42:28,830
Wait for me!

797
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:29,910
Hey, stop running!

798
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:31,430
-Don’t follow me.
-Hey!

799
00:43:01,580 --> 00:43:02,270
Lady Wuji.

800
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:08,680
Lady Wuji.

801
00:43:20,210 --> 00:43:20,990
Lady Wuji.

802
00:44:02,330 --> 00:44:05,130
It seems that Lady Wuji forgot to close the window.

803
00:44:30,630 --> 00:44:31,770
You're lucky.

804
00:44:36,750 --> 00:44:38,930
The Yang family of Gusu.

805
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,880
In good health.

806
00:44:50,340 --> 00:44:51,770
A full-term birth.

807
00:44:55,490 --> 00:44:56,290
Nepeta.

808
00:44:59,520 --> 00:45:01,860
So this is Madam Lan's real medical case.

809
00:45:04,820 --> 00:45:06,080
Hide a tree in a forest,

810
00:45:06,230 --> 00:45:07,430
hide water in the sea.

811
00:45:09,880 --> 00:45:11,340
It's indeed a smart trick.

812
00:45:14,190 --> 00:45:15,450
Young Master Yuanzhi.

813
00:45:35,950 --> 00:45:37,640
How dare a mere Green Jade Guardian

814
00:45:37,640 --> 00:45:39,550
hurt the lord of the Zhi Lineage?

815
00:45:39,860 --> 00:45:40,640
How dare you!

816
00:45:40,660 --> 00:45:42,070
You broke into the Yu Lineage

817
00:45:42,070 --> 00:45:43,470
and committed thievery.

818
00:45:43,660 --> 00:45:45,190
As a guard of the Yu Lineage,

819
00:45:45,300 --> 00:45:46,960
I have the right to arrest you.

820
00:45:48,540 --> 00:45:49,900
You?

821
00:46:32,790 --> 00:46:33,590
Guardian Jin,

822
00:46:33,710 --> 00:46:34,640
are you alright?

823
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:36,080
I'm fine.

824
00:46:36,780 --> 00:46:38,330
Miss Yun, please go back to your room.

825
00:46:38,330 --> 00:46:39,590
It's not safe outside.

826
00:46:51,380 --> 00:46:52,140
I knew

827
00:46:52,220 --> 00:46:53,350
you would come back.

828
00:46:54,150 --> 00:46:56,340
Young Master Xue, thank you for your leniency

829
00:46:56,340 --> 00:46:57,700
and giving me another chance.

830
00:46:57,700 --> 00:46:59,200
Agreeing to let you continue the trial

831
00:46:59,200 --> 00:47:01,150
was the decision of the Council of Elders.

832
00:47:01,150 --> 00:47:02,540
It's not us being lenient.

833
00:47:02,540 --> 00:47:03,600
Cut the small talk.

834
00:47:04,300 --> 00:47:06,530
Sword Wielder, you have already wasted many days.

835
00:47:06,530 --> 00:47:07,390
You must hurry.

836
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:20,770
Actually,

837
00:47:21,440 --> 00:47:23,300
you are the true Young Master Xue,

838
00:47:25,020 --> 00:47:25,480
right?

839
00:47:41,420 --> 00:47:42,120
Father,

840
00:47:42,290 --> 00:47:43,210
it's too cold.

841
00:47:43,420 --> 00:47:44,820
I can't stand it anymore.

842
00:47:44,830 --> 00:47:46,050
Didn't I teach you?

843
00:47:46,470 --> 00:47:48,650
If you don't want to be frozen, use the chant.

844
00:47:48,650 --> 00:47:49,430
But...

845
00:47:49,700 --> 00:47:50,960
But it's so cold.

846
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:52,500
I can't remember.

847
00:47:53,020 --> 00:47:54,010
You're so weak.

848
00:47:54,350 --> 00:47:56,030
You don't deserve to be my son.

849
00:47:56,800 --> 00:47:57,480
Gong Ziyu,

850
00:47:57,500 --> 00:47:58,340
come back!

851
00:47:58,550 --> 00:47:59,680
Where are you going?

852
00:48:08,780 --> 00:48:09,750
Mother!

853
00:48:11,030 --> 00:48:12,500
Help me!

854
00:48:14,680 --> 00:48:18,950
Cold air enters the clouds.

855
00:48:14,830 --> 00:48:33,130
